### Health Check (no token needed)
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair

###

### Get single customer C001
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers/C001
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair

###

### Get all items
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair

###

### Get single item A007
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items/A007
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair

###

### Get all orders
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair

###

### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:3000/api/create-order
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "C001",
  "customer_name": "Max Mustermann",
  "items": [
    { "article_number": "A001", "quantity": 2 },
    { "article_number": "A007", "quantity": 1 },
    { "article_number": "A004", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "created_via": "AI"
}

###

### Test wrong token (should return 403)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token

###

### Test unknown customer (should return order_created: false)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/create-order
Authorization: Bearer erp-secret-token-2024-umair
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "C999",
  "items": [{ "article_number": "A001", "quantity": 1 }]
}